sequenceDiagram
    participant OMS as Order System
    participant AI as AI Controller
    participant Drone as Drone
    participant UTM as UTM System
    participant Weather as Weather Service

    OMS->>AI: New Delivery Request
    AI->>Weather: Check Conditions
    Weather-->>AI: Weather Status
    AI->>UTM: Request Clearance
    UTM-->>AI: Flight Authorization
    AI->>Drone: Initialize Systems
    Drone-->>AI: System Status
    AI->>Drone: Load Mission Data
    Drone-->>AI: Mission Confirmed
    AI->>OMS: Ready for Takeoff